This directory contains all of the forcefields and templates that are supplied with ProtoMS.

opls96.ff           : The OPLS all-atom forcefield as published in 1996
opls96-residues.ff  : The protein residue templates that go with opls96.ff

solvents.ff         : Solvent templates and parameters for a wide range of solvent models (including ions)

amber99.ff          : The amber parm99 force field
amber99-residues.ff : The protein residue templates for amber99.ff
gold-residues.ff    : Protein residue templates for GOLD-like flexibility of the protein 
                      (e.g, polar hydrogens can rotate)
gaff.ff             : The General Amber Force Field 

